Threshold attributes are removed as NOS can maintain the fabric port OPER_UP state and can trigger isolation sequence based on up or down fabric port thresholds. There is no need to push down this information to SAI layer and expect a callback.

@rlhui 
Same isolation sequence is also applicable to VOQ De-Agg Chassis.

